title: Identical twins and 'carousels': Russia's election
text:
Identical twins and 'carousels': Russia's election 6:23am GMT - 02:04 
Reuters has documented numerous cases of voting irregularities that took place during Russia's presidential election that saw Vladimir Putin win by a landslide.
